1:
Yahweh reigns; he is robed in majesty;
\q Yahweh has clothed and girded himself with strength.
\q The world is firmly established; it cannot be moved.
\q
2:
Your throne is established from ancient times;
\q you are from everlasting.
4:
Above the crashing of many waves,
\q the mighty breakers of the sea,
\q Yahweh on high is mighty.
